item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - Young K - Letters With Notes (Amazon Music FLAC 16bits/44.1kHz)
item.description:
Letters With Notes (stylized as Letters with notes) is the first full-length album by Young K. It was released on September 4, 2023 with "Nothing But" serving as the album's title track.
"Let It Be Summer" was pre-released on August 25, 2023.

  5. "Bungee Jumping" - 3:22
  6. "Natural" - 2:40

  8. "Soul" (feat. Choi LB) - 3:36
